trans-unit.source: Defines custom placement parameters for a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Definerer egendefinerte plassering parametere for en <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The CustomPopupPlacement structure defines a location for a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup> control with respect to its parent, and defines how the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup> moves to become more visible when it is obscured by a screen boundary.
trans-unit.target: Strukturen CustomPopupPlacement definerer en plassering for en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup>kontrollere i forhold til overordnet og definerer hvordan <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup>flytter blir flere synlige når det er skjult av en grense på skjermen.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.CustomPopupPlacementCallback?displayProperty=fullName> delegate returns an array of these structures as custom placement options for a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup> when the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup.Placement%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.PlacementMode>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.CustomPopupPlacementCallback?displayProperty=fullName>representanten returnerer en matrise av disse strukturene som egendefinert plasseringsalternativer for en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup>når <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup.Placement%2A>egenskapen settes til <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.PlacementMode>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.PlacementMode> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup.Placement%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.CustomPopupPlacementCallback?displayProperty=fullName>
